FBIS3-49860 "dreeu012_a_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 ALBANIA Youth Forums Protest Arrest of Kosovar Leader AU1401213794 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 GMT 14 Jan 94 AU1401213794 Tirana TVSH Television Network Language: Albanian Article Type:BFN [Text] In a statement, the Democratic Youth Forum, the Albanian Students Independent Union, the student wing of the Albanian Democratic Party, and the Political Persecutees Youth League express their deep indignation and strong protest against the Serbian occupying authorities in Prishtina who, provocatively and intentionally, have arrested the chairman of the Independent Students Union of Prishtina University, Fisnik Cukaj. They appeal to all European youth bodies to raise their voices to defend their Kosovar counterparts and exert pressure so that Fisnik Cukaj and others are not murdered by the Serbian dictatorship but can enjoy the legitimate right of European citizens.
